      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for a daily driver. While the engine and transmission perform reliably, the exterior shows noticeable signs of use, including several paint scuffs, a minor dent on the rear passenger door, and some fading on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster. It has been regularly serviced, though it will eventually need new tires and a refresh of the suspension components to return to peak comfort. This is an honest car for someone who prioritizes function over flawless aesthetics.",
