    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance and daily utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, though a close inspection reveals the expected minor stone chips on the front fascia from highway driving. The body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are free of major curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the leather seating is supple and free of tears, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side. All electronic components, including the dual-zone climate control, navigation, and premium audio system, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, with a recent multi-point inspection confirming that the engine, transmission, and suspension are all performing smoothly. The tires have significant tread remaining, and the brakes offer firm, responsive feedback. This is a reliable, well-cared-for example ready for its next chapter.",
